Landing.HeroSubHeading.SubHeadingHero: Yakha, ulingise futhi uhlaziye onobuhle, izindlela, kanye ne-dynamics. Hlola i-Cell Collective ye:

Landing.SubHero.FeatureRichDescription: Ukwakhiwa kwenethiwekhi, Ukuhlaziywa nokubukwa konke, ebhokisini elilodwa.
Landing.ColumnBanner.BuildModelsDescript: Khombisa izinqwaba zezinqubo zezinto eziphilayo, kuhlanganisa amanethiwekhi kagesi, ukulawulwa kwegciwane, ukuguqulwa kwesignali, amanethiwekhi okusebenzisana kwamaseli, ama-webs okudla, njll ahlobene nezinhlobo ezihlukahlukene ezivela kubhaktheriya kuya ezigulini kuya ezimpukeni kuya ezitshalweni kubantu. Chaza onobuhle ngaphandle kwesidingo sokungena noma ukuguqula ukulingana kwezibalo eziyinkimbinkimbi.
Landing.ColumnBanner.PerformStimulations: Sebenzisa isikhathi sangempela, ukulinganisa okubambisanayo ukuze ubone ngeso lengqondo imishanguzo yenqubo yezinto eziphilayo ngaphansi kwe-extracellular ehlukahlukene kanye nemibandela yokuguquka (isib., Izifo). Qalisa amakhulu wamalinganiso wokulinganisa endabeni yamaminithi bese wenza ukuhlaziywa kokufakwayo-okukhiphayo ukuze ubone ngeso lengqondo izimpendulo zamaselula ngaphansi kwezimo ezahlukene
Landing.ColumnBanner.AnalyzeResultsDescr: Hlaziya amademu kanye nezimpendulo zezinhlelo eziphilayo ngaphansi kwezimo ezahlukene. Ukuhlaziya ukuhlaziywa kwesistimu yokuhlukunyezwa kwesistimu ukubikezela nokubeka imiphumela yomuntu ngamunye kanye nokuhlanganiswa kwezinxenye ohlelweni. Ukubikezela nokuhlola amathuba okuvuselela izidakamizwa kanye nokuhlanganiswa kwezidakamizwa.
Landing.VideoBanner.VideoBannerDescripti: Abafundi abasadingeki ukuba ngekhanda imibono yezinto eziphilayo - bangakwazi ukulinganisa futhi balingise ukusebenzisana okunamandla kunokusebenzisa isofthiwe ye-cell collective modeling.

Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase1.ClickOn: Chofoza ku- {photo} isithonjana ukudala imodeli entsha
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase1.Publish:
• PUBLISHED I-MODELS yizibonelo ezibukeziwe zontanga, ezishicilelwe ezitholakalayo emphakathini weqoqo le-Cell Collective ukuze zenzeke kanye neminikelo eyengeziwe.
  • IMITHOMBO YAMI iqukethe amamodeli akhakhiwe futhi anakho.
  • IHLANGANE NAMI yizibonelo abanye abasebenzisi ababelane ngazo ngokuqondile nawe. Sebenzisa lesi sici ukuze wakhe ngokuqondile futhi uhlaziye onobuhle nabalingani bakho (ngaphandle kokuthumela amafayela we-SBML oyimodeli emuva nangaphezulu).
  • Pheqa ngakwesokudla ukubona amamodeli amaningi!
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase1.YouMayC: Ungachofoza isithombe {photo} nganoma isiphi isikhathi ukufunda ngezici eziningi ze-Cell Collective.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.ClickO: Chofoza kusithonjana ukushintsha phakathi {photo1} (Buka Imodi) ne {photo2} (Imodi Yokuhlela). <q> <li> Chofoza kabili endaweni engenalutho ukwengeza ingxenye entsha. </ li> <li> Chofoza kabili i-Label ukuze uqambe kabusha igama. </ li> <li> Shift + kwesokudla ngakwesokudla ukushintsha phakathi phakathi noma izingxenye zangaphandle. </ li> <li> Shintsha phakathi kokusebenzisana okuhle noma okungalungile nguShift + ngokuchofoza ngakwesokunxele umugqa wokuxhuma. </ li> </ ol>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.NewMod: Izingxenye ezintsha ze-model zingabuye zengezwe ngokuchofoza lapha {photo}. Chofoza kabili ilebula ukuze uhlele igama legama.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.ToAddA: <span> Ukwengeza i-activator noma i-inhibitor, donsela uphinde uphonsa izingxenye ezivela ohlwini lwezingxenye zangaphakathi noma izingxenye zangaphandle kwibhokisi yenkhulumomphendvulwano yeDrop Component. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.ClickO: Chofoza ku {photo} icon ukuze ulondoloze izinguquko zakho.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase1.U: <span> Sebenzisa isilayidi esilula ukusetha izimo zangaphandle (okungukuthi izimpendulo zokufanisa). Amazinga angase aguquke ngesikhathi sokulingiswa ukuze ngibone ngeso lengqondo ushintsho kumadayimisho wesistimu ngesikhathi sangempela. Lokhu kufana nokushintsha imvelo yesimiso sezinto eziphilayo nokubona impendulo yayo. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase1.S: Khetha ibhokisi lokuhlola ngezansi kokubonakala {photo} isithonjana sezingxenye ofuna ukuzibona ngeso lengqondo kuGrafu Yokulinganisa. Ukuhambisa phezu kwelebuli yenkampani kuzogqamisa ukuhamba kwayo, okukuvumela ukuba uthole ngokushesha ingxenye ngaphakathi kwegrafu ematasa!
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase1.C: Chofoza {photo1} isithonjana ukuqala ukufaniswa. Ungaphinda uchofoze {photo2} ukumisa okwesikhashana ukumbumbuluzwa nganoma yisiphi isikhathi noma usethe kabusha ukufaniswa ngokuchofoza isithonjana {photo3}.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Cli: Chofoza ku- {photo} isithonjana ukudala ukuhlolwa okusha. Izivivinyo zisho kabusha ngokuqondile ngokuchofoza ilebula.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Use: <span> Sebenzisa isilayidi esilula ukusetha izimo zangaphandle (okungukuthi izimpendulo zokufanisa) kokuhlolwa. Lokhu kufana nokubeka izibonakaliso zangaphandle izinhlelo ze-biological ngaphakathi kwendawo yayo, kuthonya impendulo yayo yemvelo. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Cli: Chofoza ku- {photo} iicon ukuze uqale ukulinganisa.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Dos: <span> Amagrafu-impendulo ye-Dose angahle akhiqizwe kunoma yiluphi uhlangothi kumodeli ngokukhetha ingxenye efanelekile ye-X ne-Y-axis. Ngokuvamile, ingxenye yangaphandle imelelwe kwi-X-axis (okuguquguqukayo okuphambene) kanti izingxenye zangaphakathi zimelelwa ku-Y-axis (okuguquguqukayo okusekelwe). Amaphethini amaningi we-dose-respond angase akhiqizwe kusuka kokuhlolwa okukodwa. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.YouMayS: <span> Ungasesha amamodeli ngesihloko, incazelo, amathegi noma igama lamaphrotheni. Umbuzo owodwa uzosesha Amamodeli Ashicilelwe, Amamodeli Wami, futhi ahlanganyele nami amakhathalogi ngesikhathi esifanayo. </ Span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.YouCanC: <span> Ungashintsha umbono wakho phakathi kokubuka kuhlu nokubuka kwegridi. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.InThisM: <span> Kule menyu ungahlela iphrofayela yakho yomsebenzisi, shintsha iphasiwedi yakho, futhi ungene ngemvume. </ span>
JoyDashboardRide.joyrideStepsModelPhase2: <span> Imibandela (noma i-SubConditions) isetshenziselwa ukufanisa ukuxhasana okubambisana noma okungaxhunywanga phakathi komuntu oyedwa noma ngaphezulu obambisene nabo. Chofoza ukwengeza isithonjana ukuvula iphaneli yezimo, uhudule uphinde uphonsa izingxenye ezifanele kwi-(drop drop component) ibhokisi lezinkhulumomphendvulwano bese ucacisa ukuthi isimo kumele sisebenze noma singasebenzi. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.ClickO: Amamodeli anqatshelwe futhi ahlongozwa usebenzisa i-Knowledge Base. Chofoza ku- {photo1} ukwengeza okuqukethwe kanye {photo2} ukwengeza izinkomba. Mane nje ufake i-PubMed Identifier (PMID) ukuze ufomathile ngokucophelela futhi uhlanganise izingcaphuno. Izikhombisi-ndlela zingagcinwa ngokusho kokushicilelwa kanye nedatha yedatha. Chofoza ngokuqondile ngakwesokudla bese ukhetha ithegi ofuna ukuyengeza.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.Collab: Ukusebenzisana kuyisihluthulelo kokutholakala okusha usebenzisa indlela yokusebenza - futhi kusenhliziyweni ye-Cell Collective! Ukuchofoza ku- {photo} kukuyisa ekhasini le-Abelana, okukusiza ukuba ungeze abahlanganyeli, udale izixhumanisi ezingabelanayo futhi ushicilele ukuhlolwa.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.Select: <span> Khetha ingxenye ongathanda ukuyithutha. Ukuchofoza ibhokisi kanye ukuguqulwa kokusebenza kokusebenza (okukhonjiswe uphawu lokubomvu), futhi ukuchofoza ibhokisi kabili kunguquko yokuzuzwa komsebenzi (okukhonjiswe uphawu lokuhlola oluhlaza). Ukuchofoza okwesithathu kususa ushintsho. Izinguquko zingase zenziwe ngaphambi noma ngesikhathi sokumbumbuluzwa ukuze zibone ngeso lengqondo ushintsho kumadayimani ngesikhathi sangempela. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase2.C: Chofoza {photo} ukudala isimo sokuqala. Uma nje isimo sokuqala sidalwa, isithonjana siboniswa ngaphakathi kwephaneli yangaphakathi lezakhi. Kusuka kule kholomu, khetha izingxenye ofuna ukuzibandakanya ekuqaleni kokulinganisa (t = 0).

Chofoza {photo} ukurekhoda ukugeleza kokufanisa. Isithonjana sizophendulela oluhlaza uma okuqoshiwe kuqhubeka. Izinguquko ezimweni zokuhlola noma ukuguqulwa kwezinto, kanye nesikhathi esithile sesikhathi sokuphazamiseka kwesikhashana, sibhaliwe futhi sigcinwa ngaphakathi kokugeleza kokulinganisa, okuvumela ukuqhutshwa kabusha kokuhlolwa kokuhlelwa kabusha.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase2.Mul: <span> Ukuhlolwa okuningi kunokhethwa ngokusebenzisa amabhokisi okuhlola. Uma ukhethiwe, ungasusa, ukopishe noma uphinde uphinde uqalise ukuhlolwa ngesikhathi esisodwa. Lokhu kuwusizo ngokukhethekile ekubuyekezeni ukuhlolwa ngemva kokwenza ushintsho kumshini wokulawula umodeli. </ span>,
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase2.Col: Chofoza {photo} eceleni kwe-Flow Ukulinganisa: ilebuli ukuze udale ukugeleza kokumemeza. Ukuhlaziya ukulinganisa ukulinganisa akukwazi ukuqoshwa, ngakho-ke, izimo zangaphandle (okuyizimpendulo) noma ukuguqulwa kwezinto, kanye nobubanzi bazo (okungukuthi izikhathi ezenzekayo) kufanele zichazwe ngaphambilini. Funda ukugeleza kokulinganisa kokufundisa ukuze uthole imininingwane eyengeziwe.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase2.Onc: <span> Uma usuphethe igrafu ethulwe lapha ungalanda iGrafu Yobudlelwane Bomsebenzi njengefayela le-PNG ngokuchofoza lapha. </ span>
